headline.print_headline: FAA: Data From U-2 Spy Plane Caused Computer Issue
headline.main: FAA: Data From U-2 Spy Plane Caused Computer Issue

lead_paragraph: The primary air traffic control system around Los Angeles shut down last week because data from the a U-2 spy plane's flight plan confused software that helps track and route aircraft around the region, the Federal Aviation Administration said Monday.
